The Governing Board of the Dixon Unified School District voted unanimously to adopt a distance learning model for the reopening of school on August 10th. at it's meeting on Thursday night. This means that there will not be a physical return to school at this time. Extensive communication on the details of the start of the school year will be distributed beginning in the afternoon on Friday, July 17th. Please look for emails, letters sent home, and posts on our website and Facebook page.

La Mesa Directiva del Distrito Escolar Unificado de Dixon vot√≥ por unanimidad para adoptar un modelo de aprendizaje a distancia para la reapertura de la escuela el 10 de agosto. en su reuni√≥n el jueves por la noche. Esto significa que no habr√° un regreso f√≠sico a la escuela en este momento. Se distribuir√° una amplia comunicaci√≥n sobre los detalles del inicio del a√±o escolar a partir de la tarde del viernes 17 de julio. Por favor busque correos electr√≥nicos, cartas enviadas a casa y publicaciones en nuestro sitio web y p√°gina de Facebook.

The Rotary Club of Dixon donated to support Alicia Mattson in running her afterschool robotics program at Maine Prairie High School. The funds will help pay for UC Davis' C-Stem Studio software, to allow students to learn to code Linkbot robots.
